data.description: Escape to your own slice of paradise in Homosassa, FL with this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home on a sprawling 5-acre estate. Surrounded by peace and tranquility, this property offers the perfect retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life.    As you approach, you'll be captivated by the mature landscaping that graces the front yard, setting the stage for the natural beauty that envelops the entire property. Towering, majestic trees provide shade and add to the serenity of this picturesque setting.    The home itself is well-maintained, and it boasts several recent updates that enhance your comfort and peace of mind. A newer roof installed in 2018 ensures protection from the elements, while the brand-new air conditioning unit (installed in 2022) keeps you cool and comfortable year-round. You'll also appreciate the recently updated water heater from 2020 and the installation of all-new fans.    One of the highlights of this property is the backyard, where you can kick back and unwind by a crackling campfire. It's the perfect spot for outdoor gatherings, marshmallow roasting, and stargazing on clear, Florida evenings.    The home features a 2-car garage, offering ample storage space and protection for your vehicles. Additionally, a screened-in lanai allows you to enjoy the fresh Florida air without the nuisance of insects.    With 1,349 square feet of living space, this home provides a cozy and inviting atmosphere. It's the ideal canvas to make your own, whether you're looking for a year-round residence or a seasonal getaway.    Homosassa, FL, known for its natural beauty and outdoor recreational opportunities, is the perfect backdrop for this lovely property. It's a place where you can truly connect with nature and find solace in the serene surroundings.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this 5-acre oasis your own. This home is a rare find in Homosassa, offering a perfect balance of modern comfort and natural beauty. Schedule a viewing today and step into a world of peace, tranquility, and endless possibilities.
